LogFile.FinalText: An incredible likeness. That how many people think about Denmark's two pricesses. There are many likenesses between Mary and Marie, but as many, if not more differences. They are both from abroad, are ?? born and have both found a prince of Denmark - Mary is married with Crown Prince Frederik and Marie to Prince Joachim. Also names and looks are much alike. Both beautiful as models with long, dark hair and big brown eyes. But in spite of the many likenesses are Mary and Marie also two independent individuals who have lived and are living in each their own way which has been important to their values and characters.
